      "text": "func: \n- define their metrics / params \n- alet medium: slack, mail \n- data def: issue, time/date, sevearity, who is affected\n\nmontoring : \n- vizualization of services \n-  \n\nnon func: \n- high availability\n- low latency\n- failsafe, fallback \n- eventual consistency \n\n100,000\n1 - 1000\n\n",
