    {
      "id": "Kx9kCZCH8lASjLCeTLddl",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 543.42431640625,
      "y": 161.33335367838527,
      "width": 716.3841552734375,
      "height": 1286.4545193142355,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0H",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 486435547,
      "version": 1353,
      "versionNonce": 534970683,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1769279629137,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "design uber \n\nfunc: \nuser \n- booking the ride / cancle, update\n- enter location ; get available options ; car sizes \n- realtime updates / notif\n\ndriver \n- provide availability | location / range of operation\n- car details / capacity\n- view booking / schedule \n\n- ratings \n\n\nnon func: \n- consistency for booking \n- availability for services \n- low latency\n- surges - bookings \n- authentication ; stripe \n\nout scope: \n- fallback \n- authentication\n\n\ncore entities: \nbookings \ndriver details \nlocation\n\nAPI requests\n\nGET /search/time == {} & loc == {} & cap /size of vehicle == {} -> listings\n\nPOST /book/{bookingid}\nbody:{\ntime / date\nbooking id \ndetails\ntype : new booking, update, cancel\n\nPOST /notif/{}\n\nPOST /driver/updatedetails\n{\n   jwt\n    size of vehicle\n    hours  op\n    loc\n}",
      "fontSize": 19.418181423611102,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "design uber \n\nfunc: \nuser \n- booking the ride / cancle, update\n- enter location ; get available options ; car sizes \n- realtime updates / notif\n\ndriver \n- provide availability | location / range of operation\n- car details / capacity\n- view booking / schedule \n\n- ratings \n\n\nnon func: \n- consistency for booking \n- availability for services \n- low latency\n- surges - bookings \n- authentication ; stripe \n\nout scope: \n- fallback \n- authentication\n\n\ncore entities: \nbookings \ndriver details \nlocation\n\nAPI requests\n\nGET /search/time == {} & loc == {} & cap /size of vehicle == {} -> listings\n\nPOST /book/{bookingid}\nbody:{\ntime / date\nbooking id \ndetails\ntype : new booking, update, cancel\n\nPOST /notif/{}\n\nPOST /driver/updatedetails\n{\n   jwt\n    size of vehicle\n    hours  op\n    loc\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
